1	/**
2	 * Layerinfinite — routes/admin/trigger-training.ts
3	 * POST /v1/admin/trigger-training
4	 * ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
5	 * Check training readiness and trigger training manually.
6	 * ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
